Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.56,0:00:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会长  请进
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.86,0:00:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜香大小姐也请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.07,0:00:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,永谷小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.36,0:02:26.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.83,0:02:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊  这次也没有目击情报
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.09,0:03:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是在乘客稀少的时间段嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.86,0:03:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,干啥  室户
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.47,0:03:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是来推销新书的话  直接送到署里去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我是不会看的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.12,0:03:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀  今天不同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:22.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对这次事件我有点兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是杀人事件  不是室户先生喜欢的怪谈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又给我来这套  我可是听到一些传闻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？你是说那个无聊的传闻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  就是说听到歌声那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.09,0:03:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是诅咒之歌  死亡之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.23,0:03:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来自灵界的细语
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:45.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诅咒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,歌声吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.40,0:03:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在网上可是炒得沸沸扬扬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.88,0:03:52.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,杀人事件发生的晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从收音机和电视里传来女孩子的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.57,0:03:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会是那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.07,0:04:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个花子啊  半截怪啊啥的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,过去好像蛮有名的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这回是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,歌声被录下来流传到网上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:09.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,北村啊  你信这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  你们不信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.93,0:04:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为报道研究会的人  应该会感兴趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在毕业的前辈里  不是有很擅长这方面的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个不算  室户学长是报道研之耻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:27.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我憧憬的是真田香里学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.31,0:04:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我对这种怪论没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怪论！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  即然这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怪谈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的星球上也有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雷纳比亚的遥控人偶里有库帕幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你还下载了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么让人不舒服的歌没必要特地放给我们听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别放啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:04:58.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喔…中杉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  中杉  这边  这边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.23,0:05:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弄伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.00,0:05:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说我吗？  你从哪进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.54,0:05:30.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  你是住在附近的孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你不能随便就进别人家里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用不着担心  姐姐你有守护天使保佑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:52.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}下一则新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}连续几天  以地铁丸之内线为中心发生的连续杀人事件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.97,0:05:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}至今未能发现有力的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:02.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}搜查陷入困境
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:04.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个吧  今天在学校谈论的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}根据法医生的解剖鉴定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:11.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}迄今为止死亡的四人死因都是胸部受到重压导致内脏破裂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:19.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛  那么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真是麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛穿上写真偶像的衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别在意这些小事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.48,0:06:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有点在意那个事件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.14,0:06:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  您是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  总觉得在哪…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…  有田紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:52.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:55.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关于那个诅咒之歌的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.57,0:06:57.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被害人的死法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:07:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,据我今天听到的情报  像是被大猩猩什么的勒死的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我觉得再深入调查一下会很有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  取材费能再多拨点给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.09,0:07:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  我一定出色的搞到您要的新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:24.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了  这下就能坚持一段时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.52,0:07:29.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这边只能先放一放了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.42,0:07:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人家是有田紫苑呐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:38.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个功啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:51.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到老奸巨猾的交到个女朋友和有田紫苑一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.09,0:07:53.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有那个  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:57.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  赶紧找个理由闪人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你想去调查事件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:09.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  我差不多该告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:12.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样  正在兴头上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来  喝吧  喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我喝完就走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.42,0:08:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦  海量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就此告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧的  是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:08:59.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.65,0:09:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:55.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.96,0:09:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:09:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会是什么恶劣的恶作剧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是昨天不是出现了受害者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:04.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,时间正好是那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:06.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会是犯人的伎俩？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,干扰电波  播放歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真要和事件有关的话  新闻什么的应该会说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:16.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种传闻  警察会重视吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天要不是你姐姐来捣乱…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:22.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自己玩得那么起劲还敢说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏发生事件  可以确定大致范围了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就能找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,专家办事就是不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.83,0:10:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过与我们无关
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.55,0:10:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底是你私自开发的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  你不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.32,0:10:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国家的媒体很容易操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:04.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.53,0:11:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了  您认识受害者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.99,0:11:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.26,0:11:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…有田紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.91,0:11:17.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么室户前辈会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:25.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.55,0:11:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.84,0:11:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经无路可逃了  有田紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.79,0:12:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这不是室户前辈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.18,0:12:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…你是早宫的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一川  不对  万…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:09.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对  千川
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.07,0:12:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  有田紫苑进到这里来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没人进来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.18,0:12:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.01,0:12:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一看就明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}下一站  新宿  新宿  出口在…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先下车了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的也是？难道又要…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:56.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.85,0:12:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帝托
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.45,0:13:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  千川
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.03,0:13:15.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这边有什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.66,0:13:18.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能听到歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这可真惨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊  巴迪觉得那个事件和硫加有关吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.39,0:13:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还不能确定  但我觉得有牵连
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.77,0:13:51.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是硫加会杀人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了是危险品了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.57,0:13:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想对地球人来说肯定也很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.72,0:13:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:03.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  可疑的地方都拿出来好好调查一番
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.17,0:14:05.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.75,0:14:10.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓的黑网站  有点让人不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.28,0:14:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人给人的印象是不是差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.36,0:14:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,受害者都是短发带眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.81,0:15:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了  小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,室户  你在这干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈  我想着这身打扮犯人就会出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:54.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,傀儡木偶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:15:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目标确认
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.68,0:16:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会长  请等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.08,0:16:09.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佐佐木君  到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.59,0:16:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我解释清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会…会长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太激动对身体不好哦  中杉会长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.26,0:16:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佐佐木先生  你说出去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:23.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,胆小的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.23,0:16:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏玛朗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,社会上炒得沸沸扬扬的连续杀人事件的犯人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:32.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里逃走的傀儡木偶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,傀儡木偶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也听说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里开发的傀儡木偶并不是单纯的看护用机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.94,0:16:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我没听说是用于战争
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的以为是在制造看护用机器人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我给这研究所投了多少钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目标锁定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妈…妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目标删除
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.69,0:17:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.41,0:17:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,删除
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:24.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.93,0:17:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都是与永谷主任拥有相同特征的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.14,0:17:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是她设定的程序吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.96,0:17:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:34.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,设定了对自己撒娇的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,M程序的解析已经成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  但是出现了BUG
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还陪着你做白日梦是无法在世上生存下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的人都清楚得很
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:55.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了使傀儡木偶能够自主行动而开发的M程序是黑匣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在被打开了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.40,0:18:01.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,某国的军方研究室都没成功
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这证明了你的部下很优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你从哪搞到傀儡木偶的基础设计方案的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这你不用知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:23.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊  我教你的歌记住了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.77,0:18:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好孩子  记住了妈妈的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.66,0:18:35.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妈…妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对  是妈妈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.04,0:18:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么晚才给你调整眼睛  对不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈最喜欢你了  来抱抱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也最喜欢妈妈了  来抱抱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:18:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妈…妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.21,0:19:29.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,成功啦  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,调查下这家伙的话  能找到点线索吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  听到没
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:37.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊  那就带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.88,0:19:44.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.22,0:19:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,监护者？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:19:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:19:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是联邦的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:08.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘  马上就要下班了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.64,0:20:16.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟丢了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.58,0:20:19.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚接到部下报告
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.93,0:20:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,傀儡木偶的电波突然中断
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.96,0:20:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看情况要顺利捕捉到它很困难了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.47,0:20:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  刚才的声音是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到傀儡木偶了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.76,0:20:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.55,0:20:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玩木偶游戏可以  但善后要做好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要不然你寻找的宝物就要被人横刀夺爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.38,0:21:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,守护天使
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.17,0:21:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不相信这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.73,0:21:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.91,0:21:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能交个朋友吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.76,0:23:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人家是有田紫苑呐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.95,0:23:18.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都好热呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.37,0:23:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种酷暑去山中避暑真是不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.44,0:23:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因此  功君他们好像要去中杉小姐家的别墅了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功君内心一目了然  激动不已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.92,0:23:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这愉快的气氛被不得了的事件给浮云了  哇
